: [[John Huston]] – [[Die Ehre der Prizzis]] ''(Prizzi's Honor)''
: [[Akira Kurosawa]] – [[Ran (Film)|Ran]]
: [[Peter Weir]] – [[Der einzige Zeuge]] ''(Witness)''

